	"ART_ru_overview": "OVERVIEW",
	"ART_ru_general_a_1": "These rules are intended to define the terms and conditions that apply to all bets accepted by us. It is your responsibility to make yourself aware of these rules and the terms upon which your bets are accepted. We reserve the right to amend these rules at any time and any such amendments will then be displayed on this website. Please note that any additional information detailed in the \"Announcements\"section forms part of the betting rules. In the event of any disparity, please note that any such additional information will supersede our betting rules.",
