	"ART_ru_general_b_2": "The company relies entirely upon the information provided by the customer within their betting account. The company is not responsible for any form of misrepresentation by the customer.",
	"ART_ru_general_b_3": "When betting, members are solely responsible for their own account transactions. Please be sure to review your bets for any mistakes before submitting. Once a transaction is complete, it cannot be changed. The company does not take responsibility for missing or duplicate bets made by the client. Clients may review their transactions in the \"Statement Details\" section of the site after each session to ensure all requested bets were accepted.",
	"ART_ru_general_b_4": "In the case of any complaints, the company does not consider valid prints or receipts, which have not been recorded or stored in the company files.",
