	"ART_ru_general_e_2": "For events where injury or stoppage time is played, this is deemed to be part of regular time.",
	"ART_ru_general_e_3": "Overtime will only count where stated in the individual sport rules.",

	"ART_ru_general_f": "DEAD HEAT RULES",
	"ART_ru_general_f_1": "For markets where there is a dead heat with two or more winning selections in an event, the winnings will be reduced. This reduction is calculated by dividing the total stake by the number of selections of that dead heat. This reduced stake is then multiplied by the original odds to calculate the winnings. This part of the stake is then returned to the customer, together with any winnings. The other part of the stake is lost.",
	"ART_ru_general_f_2": "For example:",
	"ART_ru_general_f_2_1": "Stage 1 – You bet \u00245.00 on a selection at 16.0 (Potential winnings of \u002475.00)",
	"ART_ru_general_f_2_2": "Stage 2 – Your selection is in a dead-heat with another selection both finishing in 1st place",

	"ART_ru_general_f_2_3-1": "Stage 3 – Win/loss calculation: (Stake x Odd) / Number of Winners – Stake. Therefore the ",
